			<h3>Browser plug-ins</h3>

			<h4>For Firefox</h4>

			<ul class="k-links-list">

				<li><a href="https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/firebug/">FireBug</a>: it is not possible to work your code without it</li>

				<li><a href="https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/web-developer/">Web Developer</a>: a valuable set of tools that will help 

					you inspect your pages for accessibility and HTML quality control</li>

				<li><a href="https://addons.mozilla.org/fr/firefox/addon/html-validator/">HTML Validator</a>: "on-the-fly" W3C HTML validation</li>
				<li><a href="https://addons.mozilla.org/fr/firefox/addon/yslow/ ">YSlow</a>: analyzes web pages and why they're slow based on Yahoo!'s rules for high performance web sites</li>

			</ul>

			

